1, Convert the picture from other format to BMP format(monochrome mode and color depth set to be:1 ):
  convert -depth 1 -resize 160x113! -monochrome logo.png logo.bmp
  
2, Run Image2Lcd tool to get BMP image data buffer(gImage_logo) in logo.h, Image2Lcd configure as:
  Output data type :  "C language Array(*.c)"
  Scan mode        :  "Horizontal scan"
  Output gray scale:  "Single color"
  Don't select "Contains Image head information data"

  Hit "Save" it will generate "logo.h" file
   
